title: Frontlines.Fuel.of.War.Update.1.0.1-ViTALiTY-ThePiraten
description:
UPDATE NOTES

~ Holding the TAB key will display the scoreboard.
~ Server browser will not show servers that are no  longer
running.
~ "ResolveScenePosition" crash fixed.
~ Motion blur overload when redeploying fixed.
~ Autobalance - first person on a server  can  now  switch
teams.
~ Player model is no longer visible when  ascending  steep
inclines.
~ Parental controls now work. (Windows Vista)
~ Using  ALT+TAB  to  minimize  game  will  now   function
correctly.

INSTALL NOTES

~ Unpack
~ Install the update
~ Copy the crack from the ViTALiTY folder
~ Rot in heaven
